1. download nodejs the page https://nodejs.org/en/
2. install
3. terminal node -v 
4. nvm (node version manager) -> https://github.com/creationix/nvm
5. yes the comand nvm not found, copy the two ultime row the after instalation
6. vim .bashrc and paste the code
7. activation commads the nvm -> source .bashrc 
8. nvm install 6 ->install the version 6
9. nvm use system -> use the version of node install in the SO




